      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/25/437",
      "text": [
        " «تَغْتَسِلُ اَلنَّصْرَانِيَّةُ ثُمَّ تُغَسِّلُهَا."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.437 - The Imam was asked about a Muslim woman who dies and is accompanied by no Muslim women or male Muslim relatives, but there is Christian woman and Muslim men present.\nImam (as) replied: \"The Christian woman should first perform ghusl (ritual washing for herself), and then She should wash the deceased.\""
        ]
      }
    },
